message.content: The likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are "cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.NE". This is because the paper presents a new machine comprehension dataset and compares human performance to several strong neural models, which are all topics related to natural language processing, artificial intelligence, machine learning, information retrieval, and neural networks. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is "cs.CL" (Computation and Language), followed by "cs.AI" (Artificial Intelligence), "cs.LG" (Machine Learning), "cs.IR" (Information Retrieval), and "cs.NE" (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
